'''Emmabuntüs'''是基于[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]/[[Debian|Debian]]的Linux操作系统，旨在为捐赠给人道主义组织<ref>Tuxmachines.org [http://www.tuxmachines.org/node/65113 Emmabuntüs: A philanthropist’s GNU/Linux] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tuxmachines.org/node/65113 |date=20180701164923 }} 20 April 2014</ref>（如[[Emmaus_(charity)|Emmaüs]]）的翻新计算机提供一个轻量级的、对新手友好的操作系统，以延长机器的寿命。<ref>[https://www.maketecheasier.com/emmabuntus-distro-for-refurbished-pc/ Emmabuntüs – A Distro Tailor-made For Refurbished Computers] {{Wayback|url=https://www.maketecheasier.com/emmabuntus-distro-for-refurbished-pc/ |date=20180701140313 }}, '''Make Tech Easier'''</ref><ref>[http://www.everydaylinuxuser.com/2013/05/emmabuntus-2-french-revolution.html Emmabuntus 2 – The French Revolution] {{Wayback|url=http://www.everydaylinuxuser.com/2013/05/emmabuntus-2-french-revolution.html |date=20180701140300 }}, '''Everyday Linux User'''</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.heise.de/ct/ausgabe/2015-15-Emmabuntues-Schlanken-Desktop-mit-vielen-Anwendungen-2717721.html |title=Emmabuntüs: Schlanker Desktop mit vielen Anwendungen {{!}} c't Magazin |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701140242/https://www.heise.de/ct/ausgabe/2015-15-Emmabuntues-Schlanken-Desktop-mit-vielen-Anwendungen-2717721.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://linuxfr.org/news/emmabuntus-2-12-04 |title=Emmabuntüs 2 (12.04) - LinuxFr.org |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2018-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180701141808/https://linuxfr.org/news/emmabuntus-2-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

''Emmabuntüs''这个名字是''Emmaüs''和''Ubuntu''的混合。

== 特性 ==

* Emmabuntüs可以在没有互联网连接的情况下完整地安装。因为所有必需的软件包都保存在安装镜像中。安装镜像包含有多个语言包以及收费的[[编解码器|编解码器]]，用户可以选择是否安装。<ref>{{cite web|title=Features Emmabuntüs|url=http://emmabuntus.sourceforge.net/mediawiki/index.php/Main_Page#Presentation|accessdate=10 June 2013|last=Emmabuntüs|first=Collectif|publisher=Collectif Emmabuntüs|archive-date=2018-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180527043453/http://emmabuntus.sourceforge.net/mediawiki/index.php/Main_Page#Presentation|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 系统的正常运行至少需要1GB的[[随机存取存储器|RAM]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Material required for Emmabuntüs distributions|url=https://emmabuntus.sourceforge.io/mediawiki/index.php/Features|accessdate=9 November 2019|publisher=Collectif Emmabuntüs|archive-date=2019-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191109122842/https://emmabuntus.sourceforge.io/mediawiki/index.php/Features|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 安装脚本会自动执行一些步骤（比如对用户名和密码的预定义）。该脚本允许用户选择是否安装非免费的软件和一些不必要的语言包，以减少更新。<ref>Developpez.com [http://emmabuntus.developpez.com/tutoriels/english/installation-instructions/#L4 tuto post-install emmabuntus 3] {{Wayback|url=http://emmabuntus.developpez.com/tutoriels/english/installation-instructions/#L4 |date=20200604104013 }} 19 January 2015</ref>
* Emmabuntüs包含一些用于保护数据隐私的浏览器插件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://en.kioskea.net/faq/29030-emmabuntus-2-installation |title=Kioskea.net January 2013 configure parental settings |accessdate=2020-08-04 |archive-date=2013-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130323042756/http://en.kioskea.net/faq/29030-emmabuntus-2-installation |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
* 有三种类型的dock可供选择——“Basic”、“Simple”和“All”，用户可以根据自己的熟练程度选择适合的dock。<ref>{{cite web|title=Emmabuntus 2 1.04|url=http://www.superdownloads.com.br/download/125/emmabuntus-2/|accessdate=10 June 2013|work=April 2013|publisher=Superdownloads|archive-date=2020-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200225215609/http://www.superdownloads.com.br/download/125/emmabuntus-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

